    <h1>Location Pages</h1>
    <p class="description">Individual web pages dedicated to each physical branch of a multi-location business. The <strong>SEO hub for each location</strong> — combining unique NAP, GBP connection, LocalBusiness schema, and location-specific content in one page.</p>
