            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Link each GBP listing's website field to its specific location page, not to the homepage or a general /locations/ directory page. This connects the GBP entity directly to the right schema block and unique content.</p></div></div>
          </div>
